parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS brake actuator motor can cause the brake pedal to become hard to press, leading to extended stopping distances, and potentially resulting in accidents.
symptoms: The ABS light illuminates on the dashboard
the brake pedal feels hard to press
the brake pedal does not depress
the vehicle takes longer to stop
the brake system fails intermittently
and the vehicle may skid or lose control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to become detached or stuck, leading to a loss of protection for the occupant in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle dislodges
the release button sticks inside the cover
the buckle fails to lock in place
the shoulder belt does not retract or lock
the seat belt becomes loose
the seat belt retractor locks up
the seat belt does not retract to its base.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to become loose or stuck, leading to a loss of protection for the occupant in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt retractor locks up
the seat belt becomes loose
the seat belt does not retract to its base
the seat belt retractor does not release the belt.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt anchorage can cause the seat belt to become detached or stuck, leading to a loss of protection for the occupant in the event of an accident, which can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The seat belt anchorage comes loose
the seat belt detaches from the harness bolt
the seat belt hook comes undone
the seat belt clip breaks
the seat belt anchorage releases frequently when the belt is in use.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the liftgate support bolts can cause the liftgate to fall unexpectedly, resulting in injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The liftgate falls or comes crashing down
the bolt shears off
the strut expands inside the cavity
the liftgate does not stay open
the liftgate support bracket is torn
and the tailgate hinges attachment to the body is broken.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sliding door hinges can cause the door to fall off or come loose, resulting in injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The door falls off
the door comes loose
the door sticks in the open position
the door sags on its hinge
and the door hinge breaks away from the body.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The design of the gas tank does not provide adequate shield protection, which can cause the tank to rupture in the event of an accident, resulting in fuel leakage and potential fires.
symptoms: The gas tank ruptures
and fuel leaks out.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Poor handling of recalls by the manufacturer and dealers can lead to inadequate repairs, refusal to repair, and lack of communication with customers, which can result in continued safety risks and customer frustration.
symptoms: Dealers refuse to complete recalls
dealers charge customers for repairs
manufacturers deny responsibility
and customers are left with unresolved safety issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, loss of control, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle jerks or bangs when shifting
the transmission makes unusual noises (whining
grinding
or clunking)
the vehicle loses power or speed
the transmission fails to engage into gear
the vehicle surges or stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission slipping or hesitation can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, loss of control, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates when shifting gears
the vehicle jerks or bangs when shifting
the transmission makes unusual noises (whining

or clunking)
the vehicle loses power or speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission noise or vibration can be a sign of impending transmission failure, which can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or become stuck in gear, leading to accidents, loss of control, or stranding the driver.
symptoms: The transmission makes unusual noises (whining
grinding
or clunking)
the vehicle vibrates or shakes when shifting gears
the transmission feels like it's "slamming" into gear.

the transmission makes unusual noises (whining

or clunking)
